title: Deal Or No Deal
description:
The NFL Live Crew discuss Kyler Murray and Lamar Jackson wanting new deals from their teams, Lamar making it to mini camp, Russell Wilson’s comments on his new Broncos teammates, and what will success look like for Trevor Lawrence this year.
